Blog.Title: Rishabh Kumar - Google CSE
Blog.Text: I'm RISHABH SAHIL. I am a Full Stack Developer from India with over 3 years of experience in software engineering. My journey in this field has led me to contribute to several impactful open-source projects. Among these are a search engine that enhances search capabilities, an A.I Personal Assistant designed for task automation, and a WhatsApp A.I Bot developed using ChatGPT in Java. These projects reflect my dedication to leveraging technology to solve real-world problems and improve user experiences.
